(2, 1223601, 'Sisu: Road to Revenge', 'Sisu 2', 'fi', 'Returning to the house where his family was brutally murdered during the war, ‘the man who refuses to die’ dismantles it, loads it on a truck, and is determined to rebuild it somewhere safe in their honor. When the commander who killed his family comes back hellbent on finishing the job, a relentless, eye-popping cross-country chase ensues.', NULL, '/jNsttCWZyPtW66MjhUozBzVsRb7.jpg', '/yCatt8lmp3oRFEcOZF8KHhsiASQ.jpg', '2025-10-21', 'Action, War', '7.8', 154, '399.919', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-12-19 16:40:42', '2025-12-19 16:40:42'),
